{"tid":1004314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德州豪放女街頭腿開開自慰 押上警車意猶未盡繼續DIY","createTime":"2019-02-01T10:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T14:27:29.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"712b7046991fa9d785dc492374a1580404090035","tid":1004314,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3879/d3879335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3879%2Fd3879335.jpg&h=cd3dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「豪放女」妮可絲不但公然在街頭自慰，上了警車還繼續DIY！(圖／奧斯汀警局檔案照)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國德州奧斯汀一名女子周二(29日)拿著一件銀色物體， 半裸站在街頭張開雙腿自慰。期間還不斷發出呻吟聲。上述情況持續 將近8分鐘。<br />\n附近飯店職員發現後趕緊報警，員警到場後將這名「豪放女」帶走。沒想到她意猶未盡，被鎖上手銬後仍然繼續在警車上DIY！誇張程度讓人不禁搖頭。<br />\n被捕女子是26歲的妮可絲(Dovie Nickels)。當天下午她在奧斯汀 萬豪飯店附近自慰。飯店職員發現後，立馬上前阻止。妮可絲並沒有因此停「手」，只是轉移陣地到別處，繼續做她愛做的事。<br />\n期間， 她一度完全無視別人存在，自我感覺良好的在一家酒吧內自HIGH並大聲呻吟。 讓旁人尷尬到不行。 員警獲報到場後，發現妮可絲下半身沒穿褲子，於是把她鎖上手銬並帶上警車。<br />\n未料她覺得還沒爽夠，竟然在警車上繼續安慰自己！妮可絲目前被控猥褻及裸露等罪名，以3000美元(約新台幣9萬元)交保候審。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190201/1371549.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190201%2F1371549.htm&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2596dca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190201/1371549.htm</a>"},{"pid":"adb288601cc5e5eb3c5a82efdcfa48470df931d2","tid":1004314,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80ea139bab729c7150e559c8761d71b32c30ab42","tid":1004314,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9787afc36711f79d66710bacac1af65f1851ef6","tid":1004314,"uid":55758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fd0b839ea41faf938b155a4f7e6122176d79c8","tid":1004314,"uid":35930,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"做乜貼愛因斯坦出黎"},{"pid":"5d643fb8edac3aa1ab88561f984a9a2a0c71f5a6","tid":1004314,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"其實啲五官幾靚<br />\n可能吸毒吸到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48335b5a020f92cd543de3a0f40808c170500b9e","tid":1004314,"uid":58140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"成個男人咁喎ching <br />\n乜咁識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bf156cff89404abd496386b3a6a7090a57231d","tid":1004314,"uid":82815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:47:06.000Z","msg":"當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d87908512af39e03a1e6df13926156403fa6fe","tid":1004314,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"毒蟲"},{"pid":"7ac71e4ac5cbc1adf0b476c357e0dcc0af34ad6e","tid":1004314,"uid":229789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4b798fc6d3b8fc41650182797757ce12c4875f","tid":1004314,"uid":55090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"26歲好似40歲咁"}]}